TF Card Slot
============

|Product| features 2 x **TF Card (micro SD) slot**: SD0 and SD1. Both slots can address up to 32GB of memory.

.. figure:: /Media/Pi/A53/Others/TF_Card.jpeg
  :align: center
  :figclass: align-center

  *TF (micro SD) Card Slot*

.. attention::

  #) The SD0 is used only for the Lite version of Compute Module 4 that has no internal eMMC. If you use CM4 with eMMC, this SD0 will be disabled.
  #) The SD1 is used for memory extension. It canâ€™t be used for system boot-up.
  #) The product does not come shipped with the TF Card by default.
